For the first quarter of 1988, notwithstanding Article 15 of Regulation (EEC) No 2377/80 and in respect of the arrangements referred to in Articles 9 to 11 of the said Regulation:
(a) applications may only be lodged from 29 February until 7 March 1988;
(b) the information provided for in Article 15 (4) (a) and (b) of the said Regulation shall be provided on 14 March 1988;
(c) the licences provided for in Article 15 (5) (a) of the said Regulation shall be issued on 28 March 1988.
